Cost Effective
	- Pay-as-you-go
	- No upfront costs
	- No infrastructure management

Scalability:
	- Adapt to business needs
		○ Vertical or Horizontal scalability

Current:
	- Up-to-date 
		○ Microsoft responsible for Hardware Configuration, Software Patching, SW and HW upgrades, and faulty equipment

Global:
	- Easy to deploy in multiple regions
	- Provide lower latency at a minimal cost

Secure:
	- Strict security policies in physical and digital layers

Reliable:
	- Provides redundancy and fault tolerance to resources
	- Infrastructure built to accommodate disasters (backup components)
	- Data in Azure Storage is replicated


